{"tid":648252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟3】結局太震驚  觀眾信念受打擊暈倒","createTime":"2018-04-30T13:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T16:29:03.000Z","uid":117200,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c3019a636db724150e162efa99d910720b182d","tid":648252,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"美國比香港遲兩日才上映《復仇者3》，觀眾看過電影後紛紛於社交網站分享感想，雖然絕大部分都好守規矩沒劇透，但幾乎所有人都對結局表示震驚，以下節錄的反應相當有趣：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404138/org/467b78be6b24489f23ec2c5c7da0de5b.jpg/BYWdH4S9AiWXqEInG-ziqpMZgYhojIB8JY8jqSWPI6k?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404138%2Forg%2F467b78be6b24489f23ec2c5c7da0de5b.jpg%2FBYWdH4S9AiWXqEInG-ziqpMZgYhojIB8JY8jqSWPI6k%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=aee15fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「有冇《復仇者3》嘅心理輔導小組&hellip;」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404140/org/68f0bb0e388e00c23e1befbee295f1ff.jpg/l-PyAo7lYo_AcQmbNJvM_uLShBeEPOYovr--cb6_vnE?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404140%2Forg%2F68f0bb0e388e00c23e1befbee295f1ff.jpg%2Fl-PyAo7lYo_AcQmbNJvM_uLShBeEPOYovr--cb6_vnE%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=8a3bdf78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「我睇到3分1套戲開始喊，喊到完場，個人好似被挖空咗，我行唔到直線同諗唔到嘢」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404144/org/be7784fc24734c79f2cdea72e99a25ae.jpg/C3XKsAsBOLfOWkAfX87-rCFohszmqLSVHShoix0oaIs?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404144%2Forg%2Fbe7784fc24734c79f2cdea72e99a25ae.jpg%2FC3XKsAsBOLfOWkAfX87-rCFohszmqLSVHShoix0oaIs%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=6982bd1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「當《復仇者3》散場之後，全部人幾乎寂靜咁行出去，消化吓剛剛睇咗啲咩，我第一次見到咁嘅場面，永遠都唔會忘記」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404153/org/08919c970e86b48e47d21cdcc23da69a.jpg/m8ceRrdaAuMm9ShRL0lw0uNTSJoz1qTskwB_UJMAf1A?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404153%2Forg%2F08919c970e86b48e47d21cdcc23da69a.jpg%2Fm8ceRrdaAuMm9ShRL0lw0uNTSJoz1qTskwB_UJMAf1A%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=114ee5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「你哋有冇試過心碎？去到一個程度係喊唔出，咩都感覺唔到，唔想食飯、講嘢、同埋做任何嘢？《復仇者3》會令你變成咁」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404145/org/73a55133f4baabb38037d768a2637590.jpg/X7Gu79Gb1a2sSOPSN1NPUYore-srL0kZqCzP2agsz9k?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404145%2Forg%2F73a55133f4baabb38037d768a2637590.jpg%2FX7Gu79Gb1a2sSOPSN1NPUYore-srL0kZqCzP2agsz9k%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=9e103624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「我起身之後，精神上仍然唔OK，返到屋企仲諗緊琴晚套戲發生咩事，我嘔咗&hellip;我好耐未試過傷心到嘔。天呀，點會有家長覺得帶仔女去睇呢套戲係好事，佢哋會有創傷」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更有網民甚至分享某位觀眾看完《復仇者3》後昏倒被送院的場面，究竟結局有幾驚嚇先會令觀眾有咁大反應？已入場的你應該心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1404098/org/29041ae065c71cdb08c1886ff2603eab.jpg/YbnvPUvDJhCReqns5IxWYfgkc0bhoh3ywQRKvMEESrw?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1404098%2Forg%2F29041ae065c71cdb08c1886ff2603eab.jpg%2FYbnvPUvDJhCReqns5IxWYfgkc0bhoh3ywQRKvMEESrw%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=e653217b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e7a9052b7eb69abf006d304d81587aa7bd51668","tid":648252,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a848745b0ee80d9d511ccc211e0781b2f15126","tid":648252,"uid":157362,"like":4,"dis